               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>መጽሐፈ፡ቅዳሴ,Missal </p>
                     <p>I) ሥርዓተ፡ ቅዳሴ “Order of the Mass”, prefatory service (fols. <locus from="4ra" to="24va"/>)</p>
                     <p>II) አኵቴተ፡ ቍርባን, Anaphoras (fols. <locus from="24va" to="86rb"/>)</p>
                     <p>II-<locus target="#1"/>) Anaphora of the Apostles (fols. <locus from="24va" to="37ra"/>)</p>
                     <p>II-<locus target="#2"/>) Anaphora of Our Lord preceeded by an excerpt from Maṣḥafa kidān (fols. <locus from="37va" to="42vb"/>)</p>
                     <p>II-<locus target="#3"/>) Anaphora of St. John, Son of Thunder (fols. <locus from="43ra" to="48vb"/>)</p>
                     <p>II-<locus target="#4"/>) Anaphora of the <locus target="#318"/>Orthodox Fathers of Nicaea (fols. <locus from="48vb" to="56rb"/>)</p>
                     <p>II-<locus target="#4"/>) Anaphora of St. Jacob of Serug (fols. <locus from="56rb" to="62vb"/>)</p>
                     <p>II-<locus target="#5"/>)  Anaphora of St. Gregory (fols. <locus from="62vb" to="66va"/>)</p>
                     <p>II-<locus target="#6"/>) Anaphora of St. Epiphanius of Cyprus (fols. <locus from="66va" to="73ra"/>)</p>
                     <p>II-<locus target="#7"/>) Anaphora of St. Dioscorus of Alexandria (fols. <locus from="73ra" to="75vb"/>)</p>
                     <p>III) Gospel readings Mt <locus target="#26"/>:<locus from="26" to="29"/>, Mk <locus target="#14"/>:<locus from="22" to="25"/>, Lk <locus target="#22"/>:<locus from="14" to="20"/> (<locus from="76ra" to="77ra"/>)</p>
                     <p>IV) ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡ ዘሠለስቱ፡ ጊዜያት“Covenant Prayer of the Three Times” (fols. <locus from="77ra" to="80ra"/>)</p>
                     <p>V) Supplications (fols. <locus from="80ra" to="86ra"/>).</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                
               </msContents>
